text: A post shared on Facebook claims that Dr. Jill Biden, the wife of Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden, said, Whatever is on Hunters ( sic ) laptop is not important.
Says Jill Biden said, Whatever is on Hunter’s laptop is not important.

In an interview broadcast on April 4, 2021, Hunter Biden, the son of U.S. President Joe Biden, said the controversial laptop allegedly containing evidence detailing his business dealings in Ukraine could belong to him.
